CourtVision AI: Tennis Ball Tracking & Speed Analytics
Project Overview

CourtVision AI is a Computer Vision project that analyzes tennis match videos using YOLO and OpenCV. The system detects and tracks the tennis ball in real time and estimates ball speed based on frame-by-frame movement.

This project demonstrates the application of Object Detection, Object Tracking, and Video Analytics in sports technology.



